Package org.apache.zookeeper.server.backup

Class BackupPoint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zookeeper.server.backup.BackupPoint
  • public class BackupPoint
extends java.lang.Object
    Describes the point to which backups of log and snap files have been completed. It also includes a timestamp field to describe the last timestamp timetable has been backed up to (only applicable when timetable is enabled).
